name: FoodSecurityStatusVeryLowLowOrMarginal
title: Food security status very low, low or marginal
description: Uses normative values (AnswerID) related to LOINC 95264-8 Food Security Status to define results of food security assessments
purpose: (Clinical Focus: Intended usage to establish baseline food security status assessment.
